==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tartro-
<hw>Tar"tro-</hw>. <def>A combining form (also used adjectively) used in
chemistry to denote <xex>the presence of tartar</xex> or <xex>of some of
its compounds</xex> or <xex>derivatives</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tartronate</ent>⟦br⟧
